{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"491-gullino-ptaro","title":"ગુલ્લીનો પટારો","description":"ગુલ્લી પાસે એક નાનો કથ્થાઇ પટારો છે જેમાં એ ચાવી અને બટન જેવી ઘણી બધી વસ્તુઓ રાખે છે. પણ એ એ બધી વસ્તુઓનું કરે છે શું? તમે જ જુઓ! કદાચ તમને પણ પોતાનો એક ખાસ પટારો રાખવાનું મન થઈ જાય!","language":"Gujarati","langCode":"gu","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Minakshi Chandrana"],"illustrators":["Anupama Ajinkya Apte"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/491-gullino-ptaro"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/696949/size3/95a90e9213ad825d4119cacb0d9f24bf.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/696949/size6/95a90e9213ad825d4119cacb0d9f24bf.jpg"},"audio":{"src":"https://storage.googleapis.com/story-weaver-e2e-production/stories/491/audios/story/491-gullino-ptaro.mp3","cues":[[1,0,2.143],[2,2.143,2.443],[3,2.443,2.858],[4,2.858,3.272],[5,3.272,3.572],[6,3.572,4.287],[7,4.287,4.887],[8,4.887,5.716],[9,5.716,6.43],[10,6.43,7.045],[11,7.045,7.559],[12,7.559,8.573],[13,8.573,9.288],[14,9.288,10.002],[15,10.002,10.717],[16,10.717,11.431],[17,11.431,12.146],[18,12.146,12.46],[19,12.46,12.76],[20,12.76,13.289],[21,13.289,13.589],[22,13.589,14.189],[23,14.189,14.389],[24,14.389,14.889],[25,14.889,15.661],[26,15.661,16.076],[27,16.076,17.576],[28,17.576,18.005],[29,18.005,18.719],[30,18.719,21.434],[31,21.434,22.448],[32,22.448,22.863],[33,22.863,23.577],[34,23.577,24.192],[35,24.192,24.692],[36,24.692,25.62],[37,25.62,26.335],[38,26.335,27],[39,27,27.464],[40,27.464,28],[41,28,28.2],[42,28.2,28.478],[43,28.478,29.322],[44,29.322,30],[45,30,30.451],[46,30.451,31.151],[47,31.151,31.451],[48,31.451,31.851